HEADWORD: Incensant
<hw>In*cen"sant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Incense</er> to anger.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>A modern term
applied to animals (as a boar) when borne as raging, or with furious
aspect.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incensation</ent>⟦br⟧
